('Infrastructure', 'Global CSS', 'file', 'Tailwind v4 with @theme inline block defining custom colors: primary=#6B1D1D (maroon), secondary/gold=#C9A84C, cream=#FFFDF7. Custom animations: fadeInUp, shimmer, pulse-dot. Scrollbar hiding for category scroll. Print CSS (.no-print). input[type=number] spinner removal.', 'src/app/globals.css', '{"theme_colors": ["primary", "secondary", "gold", "cream", "maroon"], "animations": ["fadeInUp", "shimmer", "pulse-dot"]}', 64),

